long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Starmark is a Chrome extension that converts the repos you've starred on GitHub into bookmarks. Also, anytime you star a repo, a bookmark will be added into the "github-stars" folder in your main Bookmarks.
